                as part of an <guilabel>Optimize</guilabel> sequence,
                specifies the desired quantity to be minimized (obtained by
                using the <guilabel>Vary</guilabel> command to vary the
                control variables). </para></entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </informaltable>
      </refsection>
